1
00:04:11,990 --> 00:04:15,871
This is the first time we are having a puja in Brisbane,

2
00:04:16,831 --> 00:04:19,831
and I'm happy so many have come here

3
00:04:19,911 --> 00:04:22,151
from various places.

4
00:04:25,911 --> 00:04:27,751
You know that by puja you,

5
00:04:27,871 --> 00:04:31,751
you excite the Chakras within Me

6
00:04:33,031 --> 00:04:36,911
and you get lots of vibrations,

7
00:04:38,911 --> 00:04:40,991
and you achieve,

8
00:04:41,311 --> 00:04:44,631
suddenly, a height in your awareness.

9
00:04:47,791 --> 00:04:49,791
You do achieve that, but

10
00:04:51,151 --> 00:04:53,671
after some time they say that:

11
00:04:53,791 --> 00:04:56,231
Mother, again we come down.

12
00:04:57,231 --> 00:04:59,311
Also, they were saying that:

13
00:04:59,631 --> 00:05:02,511
"When we go to India we are all right,

14
00:05:02,591 --> 00:05:05,591
and when we come back, again we come down."

15
00:05:07,991 --> 00:05:09,831
Luckily, now we have an Ashram,

16
00:05:09,911 --> 00:05:11,511
which is a very good thing.

17
00:05:11,591 --> 00:05:14,711
To have an ashram itself is a, I must say,

18
00:05:14,791 --> 00:05:16,431
is a very, very

19
00:05:18,311 --> 00:05:19,831
positive thing because

20
00:05:19,911 --> 00:05:22,631
that is how Ganesha is established here.

21
00:05:28,871 --> 00:05:31,751
So Ashram is here for a collective living,

22
00:05:34,591 --> 00:05:38,631
but a collective living of spirituality.

23
00:05:39,551 --> 00:05:43,471
It's not just living here, but it is of spirituality.

24
00:05:44,631 --> 00:05:49,471
And we have to know certain things about

25
00:05:49,951 --> 00:05:51,911
the discipline that we have to keep,

26
00:05:51,991 --> 00:05:54,431
which is very important.

27
00:05:54,591 --> 00:05:56,751
It's not just a house where are, some people

28
00:05:56,911 --> 00:05:59,271
have gathered together to live together,

29
00:05:59,351 --> 00:06:03,311
but it has to have a discipline.

30
00:06:06,551 --> 00:06:08,911
Then only you'll be helped

31
00:06:08,991 --> 00:06:11,431
because if you do not come

32
00:06:11,511 --> 00:06:13,911
to the Ashram with this idea

33
00:06:13,991 --> 00:06:17,071
that you are going there to ascend yourself,

34
00:06:19,071 --> 00:06:20,711
it will make no difference

35
00:06:20,791 --> 00:06:21,831
whether you stay in the house

36
00:06:21,911 --> 00:06:23,911
or you go in the Ashram.

37
00:06:29,631 --> 00:06:32,791
So there are two types of meditation,

38
00:06:33,991 --> 00:06:35,511
two types,

39
00:06:36,071 --> 00:06:39,511
where one is the meditation where -

40
00:06:40,471 --> 00:06:42,711
we can call it the antarmana -

41
00:06:42,791 --> 00:06:45,311
that we meditate inside ourselves,

42
00:06:46,791 --> 00:06:50,071
to see for ourselves what's wrong with us,

43
00:06:50,911 --> 00:06:52,711
and how we have to correct,

44
00:06:52,791 --> 00:06:54,391
what we have to do about it.

45
00:06:55,151 --> 00:06:57,951
And another is bahir mana,

46
00:06:58,391 --> 00:07:00,391
which is outside,

47
00:07:00,711 --> 00:07:03,711
how we have to live outside.

48
00:07:03,791 --> 00:07:06,071
You have to have a discipline,

49
00:07:06,151 --> 00:07:08,791
which is not imposed on you

50
00:07:09,111 --> 00:07:11,391
but, very happily,

51
00:07:11,551 --> 00:07:13,351
which you have

52
00:07:15,911 --> 00:07:17,671
accepted

53
00:07:18,311 --> 00:07:20,351
and have imbibed.

54
00:07:23,151 --> 00:07:27,551
For any art, say in India, I don't know here, but

55
00:07:27,791 --> 00:07:33,671
you have to put yourself into a rigorous training

56
00:07:33,751 --> 00:07:36,751
to achieve any height.

57
00:07:38,311 --> 00:07:41,191
You cannot haphazardly move about it.

58
00:07:42,231 --> 00:07:45,711
You cannot take just easily everything.

59
00:07:46,431 --> 00:07:48,751
In Sahaja Yoga there is no tapascharya,

60
00:07:48,831 --> 00:07:51,391
there is no penance for you.

61
00:07:51,551 --> 00:07:53,191
It's all blessings.

62
00:07:53,591 --> 00:07:56,871
But one should not get lost with those blessings,

63
00:07:57,191 --> 00:08:00,271
if you have to really get into yourself

64
00:08:00,551 --> 00:08:02,871
in its full depth.

65
00:08:05,431 --> 00:08:10,831
So, for the antarmana it is important

66
00:08:10,911 --> 00:08:13,791
that you all should meditate,

67
00:08:13,871 --> 00:08:17,351
morning and evening, every day.

68
00:08:17,591 --> 00:08:21,511
Is all right even if you do not brush your teeth,

69
00:08:22,991 --> 00:08:26,751
but you must meditate is an important thing.

70
00:08:27,791 --> 00:08:30,711
That is the reason I find that in the West

71
00:08:30,831 --> 00:08:32,711
people go on catching,

72
00:08:32,791 --> 00:08:34,751
again cleaning, again catching.

73
00:08:34,831 --> 00:08:38,431
Every time I come... [I] find somebody is suffering

74
00:08:38,511 --> 00:08:40,911
from either... for some sort of a conditioning,

75
00:08:40,991 --> 00:08:43,351
or say, some sort of a baddha,

76
00:08:43,431 --> 00:08:46,871
or sometimes it's ego or something.

77
00:08:46,991 --> 00:08:48,831
It comes and goes.

78
00:08:48,911 --> 00:08:55,271
It is not something that is detached permanently.

79
00:08:57,791 --> 00:08:59,991
As we have to take our bath every day,

80
00:09:00,071 --> 00:09:03,031
we have to wash ourselves every day,

81
00:09:03,111 --> 00:09:06,751
in the same way we have to wash ourselves within.

82
00:09:06,831 --> 00:09:10,791
So meditation is the antarmana

83
00:09:12,231 --> 00:09:14,271
tapaha, as you can call it.

84
00:09:14,351 --> 00:09:16,511
But it's not such a Tapaha even.

85
00:09:16,591 --> 00:09:19,711
You don't have to go to Himalayas and sit there.

86
00:09:20,031 --> 00:09:23,351
You have to just do this meditation

87
00:09:24,951 --> 00:09:27,031
early in the morning.

88
00:09:27,431 --> 00:09:31,031
In the Sahaja Yoga system,

89
00:09:31,991 --> 00:09:35,511
I would say the best that is working out

90
00:09:35,591 --> 00:09:38,791
is in Germany and in Austria, these two;

91
00:09:40,311 --> 00:09:42,591
and also England, but not to that extent.

92
00:09:42,671 --> 00:09:46,031
I would say these two are working out the best;

93
00:09:46,111 --> 00:09:49,591
and thirdly, in Rome.

94
00:09:50,471 --> 00:09:53,751
They too have ashrams of the same kind,

95
00:09:55,271 --> 00:09:59,831
but for them it is very important to achieve

96
00:10:00,151 --> 00:10:02,231
the heights of Sahaja Yoga.

97
00:10:02,311 --> 00:10:05,551
Absolutely. Nothing is more important.

98
00:10:05,791 --> 00:10:07,751
Invariably, in all these ashrams

99
00:10:07,831 --> 00:10:09,591
I've seen people get up at four o'clock.

100
00:10:09,671 --> 00:10:11,991
I also get up every day at four.

101
00:10:12,071 --> 00:10:13,831
Then I may sleep later on,

102
00:10:13,911 --> 00:10:16,151
but at four o'clock I am up.

103
00:10:16,231 --> 00:10:18,271
They take their baths,

104
00:10:18,431 --> 00:10:20,991
get ready for the pujas,

105
00:10:21,991 --> 00:10:23,911
and then sit down and do about

106
00:10:24,071 --> 00:10:27,631
five, ten minutes puja of the photograph,

107
00:10:28,551 --> 00:10:30,471
and then meditate.

108
00:10:32,071 --> 00:10:35,111
Then they go and have some breakfast or something.

109
00:10:38,031 --> 00:10:43,551
Then when they come home from work,

110
00:10:45,071 --> 00:10:49,111
also they sit down together to meditate,

111
00:10:49,191 --> 00:10:51,591
that's the collective part of it,

112
00:10:51,831 --> 00:10:53,831
or discuss whatever is to be done, what,

113
00:10:53,911 --> 00:10:56,591
how are we to propagate Sahaja Yoga.

114
00:10:56,671 --> 00:10:59,391
They just talk about Sahaja Yoga,

115
00:10:59,911 --> 00:11:01,951
or they decide what should be done,

116
00:11:02,031 --> 00:11:03,791
what is the best way

117
00:11:03,871 --> 00:11:06,791
to solve the problems of Sahaja Yoga.

118
00:11:09,671 --> 00:11:11,911
And then in the night, before sleeping,

119
00:11:11,991 --> 00:11:14,911
invariably all of them,  all of them,

120
00:11:14,991 --> 00:11:17,591
one and all, even children before sleeping,

121
00:11:18,271 --> 00:11:21,151
soak their feet in the water,

122
00:11:21,231 --> 00:11:23,791
sit for meditation, and sleep.

123
00:11:24,711 --> 00:11:29,111
That's why I find Austria has come up so well,

124
00:11:29,991 --> 00:11:32,551
and Germans.

125
00:11:32,631 --> 00:11:34,791
You know, Germans are like that.

126
00:11:34,991 --> 00:11:37,511
If something gets into their heads,

127
00:11:37,791 --> 00:11:40,711
for them that's the most important thing;

128
00:11:40,791 --> 00:11:42,751
then they do not sort of fickle out.

129
00:11:42,831 --> 00:11:43,831
There's no...

130
00:11:43,911 --> 00:11:46,791
they don't have any compromises on those points.

131
00:11:46,911 --> 00:11:49,511
And they make their body work hard.

132
00:11:49,671 --> 00:11:52,511
Now, what is the Tapa in this thing here

133
00:11:52,991 --> 00:11:54,351
- the penance?

134
00:11:54,431 --> 00:11:58,791
That our body is used to some sort of a life.

135
00:11:58,871 --> 00:12:00,831
India also, we are all like that in India

136
00:12:00,911 --> 00:12:03,071
- everybody will get up in the morning,

137
00:12:03,151 --> 00:12:05,031
and they will sit for puja,

138
00:12:05,111 --> 00:12:06,711
or they will sit for meditation.

139
00:12:06,791 --> 00:12:07,991
I mean, that goes without saying,

140
00:12:08,071 --> 00:12:10,151
you don't have to tell them.

141
00:12:10,831 --> 00:12:13,671
Because that's the traditional thing to do in India:

142
00:12:13,751 --> 00:12:16,071
always when they get up, have their bath,

143
00:12:16,151 --> 00:12:18,511
they always do some puja,

144
00:12:19,231 --> 00:12:20,631
all of them.

145
00:12:21,471 --> 00:12:24,711
If they're Christians, also, they'll sit down and pray.

146
00:12:26,151 --> 00:12:28,191
Muslims, they'll do Namaz.

147
00:12:28,271 --> 00:12:30,911
That's a kind of a practice,

148
00:12:31,151 --> 00:12:34,471
and the breeding of the family.

149
00:12:35,591 --> 00:12:37,231
Here I find that the parents

150
00:12:37,311 --> 00:12:38,911
do not take the responsibility

151
00:12:38,991 --> 00:12:42,311
to pass on any information to children

152
00:12:42,391 --> 00:12:44,391
about disciplining themselves,

153
00:12:44,471 --> 00:12:47,031
because children are also extremely aggressive.

154
00:12:49,471 --> 00:12:51,991
They don't want to know about it.

155
00:12:53,351 --> 00:12:55,711
So the parents also dare not tell them

156
00:12:55,791 --> 00:12:57,951
that: "It is good for you, please do it this way;

157
00:12:58,031 --> 00:13:00,591
it is better that you meditate."

158
00:13:03,271 --> 00:13:05,551
They're afraid that they may lose their children

159
00:13:05,631 --> 00:13:07,111
if they tell them like this.

160
00:13:07,191 --> 00:13:09,831
Or, "You pray", or "You get up at this time".

161
00:13:09,911 --> 00:13:12,831
You dare not tell them that you get up at this time.

162
00:13:12,911 --> 00:13:15,551
This is the greatest crime in the West

163
00:13:15,631 --> 00:13:16,711
if you tell them that:

164
00:13:16,791 --> 00:13:19,471
"You have to get up at four o'clock" - amah!

165
00:13:19,551 --> 00:13:22,391
It's like the worst punishment.

166
00:13:25,511 --> 00:13:28,311
But once you start getting up in the morning,

167
00:13:28,391 --> 00:13:31,751
you'll get the habit, and then you'll sleep early.

168
00:13:36,911 --> 00:13:38,711
Then you can sleep early.

169
00:13:38,791 --> 00:13:40,711
Getting up in the morning, really,

170
00:13:40,791 --> 00:13:43,031
will help you for the whole day.

171
00:13:43,111 --> 00:13:46,591
So start this kind of a practice.

172
00:13:47,071 --> 00:13:49,591
You must meditate every day,

173
00:13:49,671 --> 00:13:52,591
and this is the reason why I find people,

174
00:13:53,071 --> 00:13:55,191
whenever I come, they're again caught up,

175
00:13:55,271 --> 00:13:56,271
something gone wrong.

176
00:13:56,351 --> 00:13:57,871
This is wrong, that is wrong;

177
00:13:57,951 --> 00:14:01,311
they're caught up here and there. Why should you?

178
00:14:01,671 --> 00:14:04,391
Day by day, you must rise.

179
00:14:04,511 --> 00:14:08,311
Day by day, you should be at a much higher state,

180
00:14:08,831 --> 00:14:12,751
and this new breeding has to come within us,

181
00:14:12,831 --> 00:14:14,911
that we are Sahaja Yogis.

182
00:14:16,191 --> 00:14:18,231
And we are not here only,

183
00:14:18,311 --> 00:14:24,591
just to have good food and to have a nice time

184
00:14:24,711 --> 00:14:28,511
or nice meetings, but we are here

185
00:14:28,631 --> 00:14:34,671
to become those unique personalities,

186
00:14:34,751 --> 00:14:38,591
which are required to raise the humanity

187
00:14:38,671 --> 00:14:40,791
to a higher state.

188
00:14:41,951 --> 00:14:45,751
So you have to be, now, responsible for yourself.

189
00:14:46,591 --> 00:14:49,191
You have to look after yourself

190
00:14:49,311 --> 00:14:51,231
and you have to tell yourself:

191
00:14:51,391 --> 00:14:53,551
"Mr. So-and-so, Mrs. So-and-so,

192
00:14:53,631 --> 00:14:55,631
please now behave yourself."

193
00:14:56,991 --> 00:14:59,671
Otherwise, Sahaja Yoga is lost to you.

194
00:15:00,071 --> 00:15:02,391
It's not going to help you much.

195
00:15:03,911 --> 00:15:08,831
We might increase in quantity,

196
00:15:08,911 --> 00:15:11,631
but quality-wise we'll be missing;

197
00:15:12,151 --> 00:15:15,831
and one attack of negativity can finish

198
00:15:15,911 --> 00:15:18,991
such a quantity that we think is too much

199
00:15:19,071 --> 00:15:21,351
- it has happened once.

200
00:15:23,631 --> 00:15:26,631
So now, all of you must develop

201
00:15:27,231 --> 00:15:32,071
that dedication to yourself,

202
00:15:34,151 --> 00:15:37,831
to find out what's your problem,

203
00:15:38,711 --> 00:15:41,551
and how you have to correct it.

204
00:15:43,071 --> 00:15:46,711
If it is done every day, I can assure you,

205
00:15:46,791 --> 00:15:49,911
you will have no problem of any kind.

206
00:15:50,511 --> 00:15:52,991
Your thoughts will stop,

207
00:15:54,471 --> 00:15:57,191
your problems will be solved,

208
00:15:59,311 --> 00:16:01,831
and you'll have no catches at all,

209
00:16:01,911 --> 00:16:03,751
because you have washed them off.

210
00:16:03,831 --> 00:16:06,071
But if you leave them on your being,

211
00:16:06,151 --> 00:16:09,751
then they grow, and they become big.

212
00:16:11,471 --> 00:16:13,791
So there should be no lethargy,

213
00:16:13,871 --> 00:16:16,551
as far as meditation is concerned,

214
00:16:16,631 --> 00:16:20,431
but joyfully you'll start doing, after some time.

215
00:16:20,591 --> 00:16:23,631
You won't be happy if you have not done it.

216
00:16:23,711 --> 00:16:26,191
But in the beginning you'll have to goad yourself,

217
00:16:26,271 --> 00:16:28,031
and tell yourself

218
00:16:28,111 --> 00:16:33,511
that this body has to be cleaned;

219
00:16:33,591 --> 00:16:36,151
but more than that body,

220
00:16:36,351 --> 00:16:39,431
this mind and intellect, both of them,

221
00:16:39,551 --> 00:16:42,031
are to be corrected.

222
00:16:42,831 --> 00:16:45,591
To be an instrument of God,

223
00:16:45,671 --> 00:16:47,711
you have to be perfect,

224
00:16:47,991 --> 00:16:49,991
perfect personality,

225
00:16:50,071 --> 00:16:52,751
otherwise we may not be able to communicate

226
00:16:52,831 --> 00:16:56,551
the message of Sahaja Yoga in the proper way.

227
00:16:58,111 --> 00:16:59,711
Many people say that:

228
00:16:59,791 --> 00:17:02,511
"We are surrendered to Mother,

229
00:17:02,791 --> 00:17:04,751
and we are surrendered to Her,

230
00:17:04,831 --> 00:17:07,911
and as surrendering we'll get everything."

231
00:17:09,231 --> 00:17:11,671
But what are you surrendering?

232
00:17:11,751 --> 00:17:14,111
Is that a clean heart,

233
00:17:14,191 --> 00:17:18,751
or a heart full of all kinds of wrong things?

234
00:17:22,991 --> 00:17:25,151
Or is that the intelligence,

235
00:17:25,231 --> 00:17:28,951
which is a very superior type of clean intelligence?

236
00:17:29,031 --> 00:17:32,791
Or else, are you coming out

237
00:17:32,871 --> 00:17:35,671
with all your arrogance?

238
00:17:39,271 --> 00:17:43,751
So though there is the Ganges of Sahaja Yoga flowing,

239
00:17:45,151 --> 00:17:49,911
still you have to have the depth of a pitcher.

240
00:17:50,111 --> 00:17:53,791
A stone cannot fetch any water.

241
00:17:56,031 --> 00:17:57,991
Same with children.

242
00:17:58,151 --> 00:18:00,151
Of course, as they'll be going to India,

243
00:18:00,231 --> 00:18:02,871
I am sure they'll form proper routines,

244
00:18:03,031 --> 00:18:07,751
and they'll form proper meditation methods.

245
00:18:11,271 --> 00:18:14,471
It is obvious that we have never had

246
00:18:14,551 --> 00:18:18,511
the sense of Divinity in the West.

247
00:18:18,591 --> 00:18:21,151
Whatever we had, whatever we got

248
00:18:21,231 --> 00:18:23,831
from the church or from any

249
00:18:24,431 --> 00:18:26,951
synagogue or something like that,

250
00:18:27,231 --> 00:18:29,791
which was only Sunday to Sunday, Sunday to Sunday;

251
00:18:29,991 --> 00:18:33,031
for a Muslim it is Friday to Friday, Friday to Friday,

252
00:18:34,071 --> 00:18:35,831
finished.

253
00:18:37,071 --> 00:18:39,751
But that has led them nowhere.

254
00:18:40,191 --> 00:18:42,991
So we have to do something about it.

255
00:18:44,031 --> 00:18:47,111
Problems will be solved in no time.

256
00:18:47,511 --> 00:18:50,031
You don't have to sit down and contemplate

257
00:18:50,111 --> 00:18:52,071
and worry: how will you solve your problem?

258
00:18:52,151 --> 00:18:54,071
It will be solved.

259
00:18:54,151 --> 00:18:55,911
But what cannot be solved

260
00:18:55,991 --> 00:18:59,071
is the habits you have developed,

261
00:18:59,151 --> 00:19:02,391
habits of lethargy.

262
00:19:03,551 --> 00:19:05,671
I can understand in London

263
00:19:05,791 --> 00:19:08,431
if the people are lethargic, but they are not.

264
00:19:08,911 --> 00:19:10,831
They have become extremely,

265
00:19:10,911 --> 00:19:14,791
extremely hardworking,

266
00:19:15,431 --> 00:19:17,111
active,

267
00:19:17,191 --> 00:19:19,471
and also dedicated.

268
00:19:19,551 --> 00:19:22,271
How they have achieved it?

269
00:19:23,831 --> 00:19:28,551
Only by knowing that this dedication brings forth

270
00:19:29,231 --> 00:19:31,911
all the cleansing, and all the powers.

271
00:19:31,991 --> 00:19:35,111
Now, supposing this instrument is not clean.

272
00:19:35,231 --> 00:19:38,231
You won't be able to even hear Me,

273
00:19:38,311 --> 00:19:40,111
it is useless.

274
00:19:40,831 --> 00:19:45,671
So our instrument has to be perfect

275
00:19:46,791 --> 00:19:50,711
to manifest Sahaja Yoga.

276
00:19:50,791 --> 00:19:55,231
If it is not, all the defects can have double effects;

277
00:19:55,311 --> 00:19:58,911
like, first it will affect you,

278
00:19:59,511 --> 00:20:05,031
you can never feel the full advantage of Sahaja Yoga,

279
00:20:05,151 --> 00:20:08,431
and secondly it will affect the people who will meet you,

280
00:20:08,511 --> 00:20:10,191
and gradually they'll find out

281
00:20:10,271 --> 00:20:12,991
there's something wrong with you.

282
00:20:13,791 --> 00:20:16,751
"Some sort of a subdued madness",

283
00:20:16,831 --> 00:20:19,191
they'll say, "this Sahaja Yoga is,

284
00:20:19,271 --> 00:20:22,711
because I don't find anything great about this man.

285
00:20:22,871 --> 00:20:25,951
He's halfway here and halfway there."

286
00:20:29,391 --> 00:20:33,551
Once you start getting deeper into your being,

287
00:20:33,631 --> 00:20:37,151
you'll be amazed that you can develop

288
00:20:37,231 --> 00:20:39,591
such capacities

289
00:20:40,831 --> 00:20:45,711
that you will be amazed at yourself.

290
00:20:47,831 --> 00:20:51,071
Of course, there are blessings, there are miracles,

291
00:20:51,151 --> 00:20:54,391
but think of your own capacities.

292
00:20:59,231 --> 00:21:02,111
What are your capacities?

293
00:21:03,231 --> 00:21:06,991
How far are you able to do

294
00:21:07,151 --> 00:21:11,031
something about curing people?

295
00:21:13,231 --> 00:21:15,551
We have few people in Bombay,

296
00:21:15,631 --> 00:21:18,231
and very few people in Pune also.

297
00:21:18,711 --> 00:21:21,711
But they are available for curing.

298
00:21:22,071 --> 00:21:26,631
Some of them are going to villages.

299
00:21:26,791 --> 00:21:31,191
Now they have asked Me to give them a jeep,

300
00:21:31,471 --> 00:21:34,911
so they could take a music party to the villages

301
00:21:35,071 --> 00:21:37,551
and sing there,

302
00:21:39,711 --> 00:21:42,031
and achieve

303
00:21:43,191 --> 00:21:46,271
a greater number of Sahaja Yogis.

304
00:21:46,431 --> 00:21:49,471
But when they come back, immediately,

305
00:21:49,551 --> 00:21:52,351
whether they come in the daytime or in the night,

306
00:21:52,431 --> 00:21:54,831
immediately they wash their feet

307
00:21:54,911 --> 00:21:56,911
before the photograph.

308
00:21:58,511 --> 00:22:00,991
Also to protect yourself,

309
00:22:01,071 --> 00:22:03,711
you have to give yourself a bandhan,

310
00:22:03,791 --> 00:22:04,711
all the time.

311
00:22:04,791 --> 00:22:06,831
It is not you should say: "Now, I'm all right."

312
00:22:06,911 --> 00:22:08,911
You should not say that: "I am perfect."

313
00:22:08,991 --> 00:22:10,911
You should not say: "Now I'm a Sahaja Yogi."

314
00:22:10,991 --> 00:22:12,711
Never, never think like that.

315
00:22:12,791 --> 00:22:14,911
The moment you start thinking you are perfect,

316
00:22:14,991 --> 00:22:16,911
you are finished.

317
00:22:19,391 --> 00:22:23,191
So before going out, you must give a proper bandhan.

318
00:22:23,591 --> 00:22:26,591
Also before sleeping you must give a proper bandhan.

319
00:22:26,871 --> 00:22:30,791
Put your attention to your Sahasrara and then sleep.

320
00:22:33,631 --> 00:22:36,751
It's very amazing how things work out.

321
00:22:37,391 --> 00:22:39,911
Immediately you will know a person

322
00:22:39,991 --> 00:22:43,711
is meditating or not, immediately.

323
00:22:44,471 --> 00:22:46,951
It's like he is a person who

324
00:22:47,111 --> 00:22:50,111
has given a bath to the child.

325
00:22:53,151 --> 00:22:55,831
Though he has given a bath to the child,

326
00:22:55,911 --> 00:22:57,271
still he has not taken a bath.

327
00:22:57,351 --> 00:22:59,991
You can make it out, the difference between the two.

328
00:23:01,791 --> 00:23:04,831
In the same way, those who have been meditating

329
00:23:04,911 --> 00:23:07,151
every day, morning and evening,

330
00:23:07,231 --> 00:23:08,751
not much time needed.

331
00:23:08,831 --> 00:23:10,311
You see, we waste all our time

332
00:23:10,391 --> 00:23:12,071
in something nonsensical.

333
00:23:15,391 --> 00:23:21,391
When there is complete understanding of yourself,

334
00:23:21,591 --> 00:23:25,471
and complete understanding of these vibrations,

335
00:23:26,991 --> 00:23:32,671
then only you can handle them properly.

336
00:23:32,871 --> 00:23:35,551
All this knowledge is for you.

337
00:23:36,191 --> 00:23:38,711
Is absolutely free as you know,

338
00:23:38,791 --> 00:23:41,991
and all this mastery can be yours.

339
00:23:42,071 --> 00:23:43,831
So do not just get satisfied:

340
00:23:43,911 --> 00:23:47,391
"All right, today's Sunday, we'll go to the church,

341
00:23:49,071 --> 00:23:52,711
take the hymn book, let us sing this hymn number

342
00:23:52,791 --> 00:23:55,791
such-and-such, again sit down, get up, sit down."

343
00:23:57,631 --> 00:24:00,591
Come back home just the same.

344
00:24:02,351 --> 00:24:08,071
So today I have really thought of telling all of you

345
00:24:08,151 --> 00:24:12,471
that you have to develop the depth within yourself.

346
00:24:15,711 --> 00:24:19,271
And if you cannot develop that depth,

347
00:24:19,351 --> 00:24:22,751
then you are still a mediocre.

348
00:24:24,631 --> 00:24:30,191
Actually all these great secrets about the Goddess

349
00:24:30,271 --> 00:24:34,471
or Her powers, were not told to anyone like that.

350
00:24:34,791 --> 00:24:36,071
Never.

351
00:24:37,151 --> 00:24:43,071
Only when they had completed their oneness

352
00:24:44,431 --> 00:24:49,351
- I would say the full idea, full understanding

353
00:24:49,791 --> 00:24:52,711
between the oneness of God

354
00:24:52,791 --> 00:24:55,831
and your relationship with that,

355
00:24:56,791 --> 00:24:59,151
absolutely –

356
00:25:00,271 --> 00:25:04,391
nobody would do anything before that.

357
00:25:06,711 --> 00:25:10,351
Now the days are, of Sahaja Yoga, are so simple

358
00:25:10,511 --> 00:25:12,831
that as soon as you get Realization,

359
00:25:12,911 --> 00:25:15,791
you can start giving Realization to others.

360
00:25:16,231 --> 00:25:17,951
Immediately.

361
00:25:18,511 --> 00:25:19,911
Just under your hand you will see

362
00:25:19,991 --> 00:25:21,551
the Kundalini will move.

363
00:25:21,631 --> 00:25:23,111
You put your hand on somebody's head,

364
00:25:23,191 --> 00:25:26,071
and you'll find that person gets realization.

365
00:25:28,671 --> 00:25:30,111
It's a fact.

366
00:25:30,191 --> 00:25:32,511
It just works that way.

367
00:25:32,591 --> 00:25:35,551
But that means, for many:

368
00:25:35,631 --> 00:25:37,511
"Oh, there's nothing to be done.

369
00:25:37,591 --> 00:25:38,951
After all, is all done by Mother,

370
00:25:39,031 --> 00:25:41,351
we have just achieved something."

371
00:25:43,791 --> 00:25:46,991
You can always understand that

372
00:25:47,071 --> 00:25:50,711
Mother can only work out a very good instrument,

373
00:25:51,831 --> 00:25:54,311
and not a weak instrument.

374
00:25:54,591 --> 00:26:01,551
So now, we have some very great Sahaja Yogis

375
00:26:01,831 --> 00:26:04,671
who have gone very deep into it.

376
00:26:04,791 --> 00:26:07,671
Invariably, whenever I asked,

377
00:26:07,751 --> 00:26:09,831
they say: "Mother, every day we worship.

378
00:26:09,911 --> 00:26:13,471
We worship morning and evening, every way, day.

379
00:26:13,551 --> 00:26:15,831
We either wash our feet

380
00:26:15,911 --> 00:26:17,711
and sit down before Your photograph

381
00:26:17,791 --> 00:26:19,631
and worship Your photograph,

382
00:26:19,711 --> 00:26:22,231
or else in the morning time also

383
00:26:22,311 --> 00:26:24,911
we do something like that."

384
00:26:24,991 --> 00:26:29,271
And amazingly, you can make them out immediately.

385
00:26:31,031 --> 00:26:34,991
There may be six hundred people at the airport,

386
00:26:37,511 --> 00:26:39,431
but immediately I know

387
00:26:39,511 --> 00:26:42,871
who has been meditating every day.

388
00:26:47,751 --> 00:26:51,151
Now, it is for us.

389
00:26:51,231 --> 00:26:54,231
We have been doing Sahaja Yoga for the last,

390
00:26:54,311 --> 00:26:56,751
now, more than twenty years,

391
00:26:57,231 --> 00:26:59,751
and now we are entering into twenty-first year,

392
00:26:59,831 --> 00:27:02,831
we can say; but I'm ready, you see, it is like that,

393
00:27:02,911 --> 00:27:07,791
because now it was 1970, and now it is 1990,

394
00:27:08,311 --> 00:27:12,351
so it is all this thing, plus ninety-one.

395
00:27:15,591 --> 00:27:17,711
So much time we have had.

396
00:27:17,791 --> 00:27:18,951
Of course, I would say,

397
00:27:19,031 --> 00:27:21,871
you didn't get your Realization at that time;

398
00:27:21,951 --> 00:27:26,071
but whatever time you got the Realization,

399
00:27:27,591 --> 00:27:30,911
I did not judge how far you were in it.

400
00:27:30,991 --> 00:27:33,831
I said: "First let them have their Realization."

401
00:27:33,911 --> 00:27:36,471
They got their Realization.

402
00:27:36,791 --> 00:27:39,551
So once they got their Realization, you see,

403
00:27:39,991 --> 00:27:43,471
people who have really

404
00:27:46,071 --> 00:27:48,911
felt the responsibility,

405
00:27:48,991 --> 00:27:51,151
from the very first day they got to it,

406
00:27:51,231 --> 00:27:52,471
from the very first day.

407
00:27:52,551 --> 00:27:54,991
I didn't have to tell them.

408
00:27:55,071 --> 00:27:59,231
I'm not talking about Indians, I'm talking about others.

409
00:28:01,231 --> 00:28:03,431
And they have done, they have shown

410
00:28:03,511 --> 00:28:06,551
tremendous improvement, tremendous.

411
00:28:08,231 --> 00:28:10,911
We have been sending you Indian boys from there,

412
00:28:10,991 --> 00:28:12,711
Indian girls from there,

413
00:28:12,791 --> 00:28:15,431
just for you to know that

414
00:28:15,511 --> 00:28:19,671
they can also help you in Sahaja Yoga.

415
00:28:20,311 --> 00:28:22,471
Definitely can help you.

416
00:28:22,551 --> 00:28:25,351
You have to have a proper type of a person,

417
00:28:25,631 --> 00:28:29,471
and you'll be amazed at the way they are,

418
00:28:29,551 --> 00:28:32,671
that they can impart everything,

419
00:28:32,991 --> 00:28:37,591
and they are least bothered about their ego.

420
00:28:37,711 --> 00:28:39,551
There's no ego at all.

421
00:28:43,351 --> 00:28:47,711
So you are not achieving all this for your ego.

422
00:28:47,791 --> 00:28:50,591
You are achieving it because

423
00:28:52,311 --> 00:28:54,671
you are a seeker,

424
00:28:54,751 --> 00:28:57,391
and now you have become a Sahaja Yogi.

425
00:28:57,631 --> 00:29:00,191
So it is to be understood that it's not

426
00:29:00,271 --> 00:29:03,631
something like a advantage in money wise,

427
00:29:03,711 --> 00:29:05,711
or something that I have to have a power,

428
00:29:05,791 --> 00:29:06,831
this, that;

429
00:29:06,911 --> 00:29:08,911
because if you do not meditate,

430
00:29:08,991 --> 00:29:11,751
your attention will go to such things.

431
00:29:12,311 --> 00:29:14,191
Immediately you'll start thinking:

432
00:29:14,271 --> 00:29:16,591
Can I become the leader?

433
00:29:16,671 --> 00:29:20,831
All right, if not: "Should I debase the leader?

434
00:29:20,911 --> 00:29:22,831
How can I insult him?

435
00:29:22,911 --> 00:29:26,191
How can I fight for that? How can I do that?

436
00:29:26,271 --> 00:29:28,311
How can I work it out this way?"

437
00:29:28,391 --> 00:29:30,311
You try to insult also.

438
00:29:30,391 --> 00:29:34,191
If not possible, you might use violence sometimes,

439
00:29:34,271 --> 00:29:36,111
anger,

440
00:29:37,791 --> 00:29:40,551
because you are not yet, I should say,

441
00:29:40,631 --> 00:29:42,631
that much evolve, evolved,

442
00:29:42,711 --> 00:29:45,711
so much mature, so much wiser.

443
00:29:45,791 --> 00:29:47,991
So now, what you have to do

444
00:29:48,071 --> 00:29:50,991
is to... at the very

445
00:29:51,071 --> 00:29:53,711
first shot when you get up in the morning,

446
00:29:53,791 --> 00:29:55,831
you first say that: "Let me see,

447
00:29:55,911 --> 00:29:58,871
what is my responsibility as a Sahaja Yogi?"

448
00:30:01,791 --> 00:30:04,911
After some time you will start enjoying it,

449
00:30:04,991 --> 00:30:09,151
because it will give you such tremendous powers,

450
00:30:09,231 --> 00:30:12,471
such tremendous experience.

451
00:30:14,311 --> 00:30:19,511
Now then, you just sit down with very humble mind,

452
00:30:19,591 --> 00:30:22,831
and first of all say: "Mother, if I have any ego, please take away.

453
00:30:22,911 --> 00:30:24,711
Mother, if I have any conditioning,

454
00:30:24,791 --> 00:30:25,911
please take away; because

455
00:30:25,991 --> 00:30:27,471
I'm a seeker out and out,

456
00:30:27,551 --> 00:30:28,831
I don't want all these things."

457
00:30:28,911 --> 00:30:30,751
But if you do not meditate,

458
00:30:30,831 --> 00:30:34,751
then this Mr. Ego will secretly crawl upon you,

459
00:30:34,831 --> 00:30:36,911
and you may try to become the leader,

460
00:30:36,991 --> 00:30:39,551
or some sort of an assertion you'll do,

461
00:30:39,631 --> 00:30:45,191
some sort of a stupid ego actions,

462
00:30:45,271 --> 00:30:47,551
which we have many in Sahaja Yoga.

463
00:30:47,631 --> 00:30:49,151
If you write them down,

464
00:30:49,231 --> 00:30:52,951
you will not know how to stop laughing.

465
00:30:55,431 --> 00:30:59,871
So to warn yourself, I would say that

466
00:30:59,951 --> 00:31:03,991
the only way to protect yourself is to do

467
00:31:04,071 --> 00:31:06,471
the meditation in the morning and evening,

468
00:31:06,551 --> 00:31:10,951
and also to keep yourself in complete bandhan.

469
00:31:16,551 --> 00:31:20,671
Yours is a very important role

470
00:31:20,751 --> 00:31:24,271
and a very important time,

471
00:31:24,351 --> 00:31:27,631
extremely important.

472
00:31:27,711 --> 00:31:29,951
You have no idea,

473
00:31:30,031 --> 00:31:33,951
that in the history of spirituality

474
00:31:34,031 --> 00:31:38,791
no one could do so much as you can do.

475
00:31:40,431 --> 00:31:44,471
So, if you really

476
00:31:46,391 --> 00:31:49,631
do the Antarmana,

477
00:31:49,711 --> 00:31:53,351
if you really see inside yourself,

478
00:31:53,431 --> 00:31:57,511
while meditating you see yourself, your chakras and all that,

479
00:31:57,591 --> 00:32:00,551
and then you find out this introspection:

480
00:32:00,631 --> 00:32:02,511
Why am I like this?

481
00:32:02,591 --> 00:32:04,871
Just separate from yourself, see for yourself:

482
00:32:04,991 --> 00:32:08,631
"Why am I like this? Why I did like this?

483
00:32:08,711 --> 00:32:12,791
Why do I think like this? Who am I?"

484
00:32:14,991 --> 00:32:17,751
These questions when answered,

485
00:32:17,831 --> 00:32:21,751
you will know all your worth, your value.

486
00:32:27,391 --> 00:32:31,071
I do not know how much I should stress,

487
00:32:31,151 --> 00:32:33,831
how much more is needed to stress

488
00:32:33,911 --> 00:32:38,031
the importance of meditation, every day.

489
00:32:39,351 --> 00:32:40,751
Like these advertisements you see,

490
00:32:40,791 --> 00:32:43,831
every day they just go on bombarding

491
00:32:43,911 --> 00:32:45,911
on your head, and:

492
00:32:45,991 --> 00:32:50,591
Buy this, buy that, buy, buy, buy, buy, buy.

493
00:32:50,831 --> 00:32:52,631
It acts.

494
00:32:53,911 --> 00:32:56,711
In the same way, you have to every day

495
00:32:56,791 --> 00:32:58,991
bombard yourself: "Now, meditation.

496
00:32:59,071 --> 00:33:01,711
Get to meditation. Get to meditation."

497
00:33:01,791 --> 00:33:04,671
Then you'll be surprised

498
00:33:04,791 --> 00:33:08,031
that when you'll go out, you'll see something beautiful;

499
00:33:08,111 --> 00:33:10,671
immediately you'll get into thoughtless awareness.

500
00:33:10,751 --> 00:33:12,911
Don't have to do.

501
00:33:13,471 --> 00:33:16,791
As soon as you'll meet a Sahaja Yogi, immediately into thoughtless;

502
00:33:16,871 --> 00:33:20,111
the other person, you both will go.

503
00:33:20,991 --> 00:33:24,991
Everything you start enjoying in a very different manner.

504
00:33:25,151 --> 00:33:27,911
And such beautiful feelings come in,

505
00:33:27,991 --> 00:33:32,311
such beautiful security is built up

506
00:33:34,671 --> 00:33:37,391
that you are surprised:

507
00:33:37,471 --> 00:33:39,751
"How I could be like that?

508
00:33:39,791 --> 00:33:44,191
How I could feel these securities just expressing

509
00:33:44,271 --> 00:33:47,791
themselves in such a beautiful manner?"

510
00:33:48,311 --> 00:33:54,151
Because if you are, say, washed and clean

511
00:33:54,231 --> 00:33:56,471
- simple thing, everyday life –

512
00:33:57,831 --> 00:34:00,751
then before touching any, everything you are careful

513
00:34:00,831 --> 00:34:03,631
that you don't again spoil them.

514
00:34:04,751 --> 00:34:09,311
If there's a sari, which is dirty, absolutely dirty,

515
00:34:09,391 --> 00:34:12,751
then if there are two spots or hundred spots,

516
00:34:12,831 --> 00:34:14,551
makes no difference.

517
00:34:15,071 --> 00:34:16,991
But when it is absolutely clean, then

518
00:34:17,071 --> 00:34:20,151
even the slightest spot you can get worried,

519
00:34:20,231 --> 00:34:22,591
because everybody will see that.

520
00:34:25,031 --> 00:34:26,791
In the same way,

521
00:34:26,871 --> 00:34:29,431
unless and until you cleanse yourself every day,

522
00:34:29,511 --> 00:34:32,471
you will not know what's wrong with you.

523
00:34:36,911 --> 00:34:41,671
I hope you'll pay full attention to what I've said here today,

524
00:34:41,751 --> 00:34:44,831
with full attention

525
00:34:46,351 --> 00:34:50,271
on your inner being

526
00:34:50,951 --> 00:34:53,391
projecting out,

527
00:34:55,111 --> 00:34:57,831
like a witness to yourself.

528
00:34:59,031 --> 00:35:01,831
Just see how you talk to others:

529
00:35:02,151 --> 00:35:04,231
"Why should I talk like that?

530
00:35:04,311 --> 00:35:06,831
What is the need to talk?"

531
00:35:07,311 --> 00:35:09,591
And then you'll start understanding

532
00:35:09,671 --> 00:35:11,511
that behind all this

533
00:35:11,591 --> 00:35:15,791
is some sort of a funny thing going on in my brain,

534
00:35:20,271 --> 00:35:23,351
and this brain has to be corrected

535
00:35:23,431 --> 00:35:25,231
- Very important.

536
00:35:25,471 --> 00:35:31,911
Now, at the end of the day we should find out:

537
00:35:31,991 --> 00:35:36,071
What good things I have done for Sahaja Yoga?

538
00:35:38,991 --> 00:35:43,871
Also, we can find out, "How I have been

539
00:35:43,951 --> 00:35:48,031
not up to the point in Sahaja Yoga?"

540
00:35:51,711 --> 00:35:54,391
If it could be done,

541
00:35:56,791 --> 00:36:00,551
you find out: "How far I have gone

542
00:36:01,991 --> 00:36:06,711
with these powers to spread Sahaja Yoga?

543
00:36:07,231 --> 00:36:10,271
How far I can go?"

544
00:36:10,391 --> 00:36:13,071
It's really remarkable because,

545
00:36:13,151 --> 00:36:18,391
as I told you, in Austria we have some boys

546
00:36:18,711 --> 00:36:22,711
who are all the time researching about Sahaja Yoga.

547
00:36:23,911 --> 00:36:26,711
They have read the book of Adi Shankaracharya,

548
00:36:26,791 --> 00:36:29,591
which I have not yet read.

549
00:36:30,591 --> 00:36:32,511
They have read all kinds of things,

550
00:36:32,631 --> 00:36:35,591
just to find out how far they are,

551
00:36:35,671 --> 00:36:37,191
and as a result

552
00:36:37,271 --> 00:36:41,351
they themselves went on developing

553
00:36:41,471 --> 00:36:45,271
very, very deep into their beings;

554
00:36:45,431 --> 00:36:48,391
but the way, you see,

555
00:36:48,471 --> 00:36:52,991
you go on developing deep, deep, deep, deep, deep,

556
00:36:53,071 --> 00:36:56,631
and you'll be amazed the deeper you go,

557
00:36:56,711 --> 00:37:00,471
you won't show off, you won't show off.

558
00:37:00,551 --> 00:37:02,711
You'll just emit.

559
00:37:02,791 --> 00:37:06,671
Like, one gentleman once came to My house

560
00:37:08,551 --> 00:37:12,911
and they said, "Mother, some cooler has come inside.

561
00:37:13,071 --> 00:37:16,671
It looks some cooler has come inside. Ya, ya, there's a cooler coming."

562
00:37:16,751 --> 00:37:20,391
He didn't say anything, didn't do anything.

563
00:37:21,071 --> 00:37:22,751
Just walking inside the house:

564
00:37:22,831 --> 00:37:25,751
Some cooler has come.

565
00:37:26,991 --> 00:37:28,831
You just felt, you know;

566
00:37:28,911 --> 00:37:31,551
like in the forest if you go,

567
00:37:31,631 --> 00:37:36,271
and you find complete silence, even the birds are not twittering,

568
00:37:36,351 --> 00:37:38,991
then know there's a tiger sitting there.

569
00:37:39,071 --> 00:37:43,511
Tiger doesn't do anything; it's just sleeping maybe, poor thing.

570
00:37:43,591 --> 00:37:47,231
But the whole place is awed by his presence, you see.

571
00:37:47,351 --> 00:37:51,151
In the same way, a Sahaja Yogi, anywhere, will stand out.

572
00:37:51,231 --> 00:37:52,911
Look at these saints, they didn't know

573
00:37:52,991 --> 00:37:54,911
how to raise even the Kundalini,

574
00:37:54,991 --> 00:37:57,871
but they were very pure people.

575
00:37:58,911 --> 00:38:00,751
They never raised anybody's Kundalini.

576
00:38:00,831 --> 00:38:02,711
They never gave Realization to anyone.

577
00:38:02,791 --> 00:38:04,711
They were extremely pure people.

578
00:38:04,791 --> 00:38:08,231
There was no impurity left in them.

579
00:38:08,311 --> 00:38:11,591
And so, how much they could produce:

580
00:38:11,671 --> 00:38:14,591
what poetry, what work,

581
00:38:14,671 --> 00:38:19,831
what spiritual, spiritual ideas,

582
00:38:19,911 --> 00:38:23,511
what sayings; I mean, tremendous –

583
00:38:23,591 --> 00:38:27,351
such depth in whatever they did,

584
00:38:27,631 --> 00:38:29,951
such effectiveness.

585
00:38:30,111 --> 00:38:32,911
Now, we are here to gain our spirituality,

586
00:38:32,991 --> 00:38:34,751
not to gain money,

587
00:38:34,791 --> 00:38:39,271
not to gain positions,

588
00:38:39,351 --> 00:38:43,431
powers - nothing. We are here to gain our spirituality,

589
00:38:43,511 --> 00:38:47,551
and in that spirituality, it's all there.

590
00:38:50,991 --> 00:38:53,551
All the satisfaction,

591
00:38:54,151 --> 00:38:55,791
everything is there.

592
00:38:55,911 --> 00:38:59,351
It will have an effect on the children.

593
00:39:01,751 --> 00:39:05,751
It will have an effect on the surroundings,

594
00:39:05,831 --> 00:39:10,071
in every way, and the personality.

595
00:39:12,991 --> 00:39:16,351
So it's not a question also individuals doing that,

596
00:39:16,431 --> 00:39:19,911
but collectively doing it.

597
00:39:21,951 --> 00:39:25,391
The collective should look a beautiful thing.

598
00:39:25,471 --> 00:39:29,391
So you should have, I would say, in an ashram,

599
00:39:29,511 --> 00:39:32,471
a collective meditation.

600
00:39:34,311 --> 00:39:36,911
In Austria they do it early in the morning,

601
00:39:36,991 --> 00:39:40,111
four o'clock, collectively.

602
00:39:40,471 --> 00:39:41,911
So they know how many are there,

603
00:39:41,991 --> 00:39:44,631
and how many are missing, this, that.

604
00:39:44,711 --> 00:39:47,711
But I said: "Don't point out. Let's see."

605
00:39:47,791 --> 00:39:50,191
When those who have been doing meditation like that

606
00:39:50,271 --> 00:39:53,711
rise so high, others start following them.

607
00:39:55,191 --> 00:39:58,231
So don't think about others: what time he got up.

608
00:39:58,311 --> 00:40:00,551
It's I; I have to look after myself.

609
00:40:00,631 --> 00:40:04,951
It's very selfish: Swarth.

610
00:40:05,031 --> 00:40:07,391
You have to know the meaning of Swa

611
00:40:07,471 --> 00:40:09,111
- that is selfishness –

612
00:40:09,191 --> 00:40:12,711
and when you know that meaning, then you are not bothered

613
00:40:12,791 --> 00:40:16,711
whatsoever anybody might say, whatsoever anyone may try to do.

614
00:40:16,791 --> 00:40:18,751
Supposing your husband is funny:

615
00:40:18,831 --> 00:40:21,351
Oh, doesn't matter. He'll come round.

616
00:40:21,431 --> 00:40:24,911
Supposing your wife is funny: Doesn't matter, she'll come round.

617
00:40:24,991 --> 00:40:28,831
Is nothing important. To you, this is the most important thing to do,

618
00:40:28,911 --> 00:40:30,911
and all those who have thought like this

619
00:40:30,991 --> 00:40:32,951
and have acted like this,

620
00:40:33,031 --> 00:40:35,871
were above everything.

621
00:40:35,991 --> 00:40:39,071
Nothing can put them down.

622
00:40:39,231 --> 00:40:42,231
So, today is the first day of Brisbane.

623
00:40:42,311 --> 00:40:45,991
I bless you all, that you should have

624
00:40:46,071 --> 00:40:49,311
this full idea about yourself,

625
00:40:49,431 --> 00:40:51,431
why you are on this earth,

626
00:40:51,511 --> 00:40:54,991
and what great work you are supposed to do.

627
00:40:55,071 --> 00:40:57,231
Each one of you is capable.

628
00:40:57,311 --> 00:40:59,231
Each one of you can do it,

629
00:40:59,311 --> 00:41:01,511
but you... I would request you

630
00:41:01,591 --> 00:41:05,631
that you imbibe these qualities within you,

631
00:41:05,711 --> 00:41:07,231
which are already there.

632
00:41:07,311 --> 00:41:10,231
I mean, I wouldn't say "imbibe", but you manifest them,

633
00:41:10,311 --> 00:41:12,391
and once you start manifesting,

634
00:41:12,471 --> 00:41:15,471
see your temperament how it is.

635
00:41:15,591 --> 00:41:18,391
We'll look after your children; don't worry.

636
00:41:18,471 --> 00:41:20,471
May God bless you.

